## Coding Conventions

### Commit Message Format
```
<type>(<scope>): <description> (#<issue>)
```

**Types:** `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`

**Examples:**
```
feat(api): add retry logic (#35)
fix(mapper): handle null values (#42)
docs(readme): update installation steps (#18)
```

